      <num>SEC. 2.10</num>
      <heading>Same—Casual employees</heading>
      <content>
        <p>The director of finance is authorized to disburse warrants for the payment of all
               accrued wages earned by casual employees on completion of work or services performed.</p>
        <p>(Code 1938, Sec. 101; Ord. No. 175.197, 1/14/53.)</p>
      </content>
